.TH mana
.SH NAME
mana-req
.SH DESCRIPTION
The mana requirement specifies the required value for the mana for the object.
.SH PARAMETERS
.P
* value
.br
Specifies the required value of  mana points.
.P
* less
.br
Specifies wheter actual mana value should be less(true) or more(false) then value in the requirement.
.P
* charge
.br
Specifies wheter required mana value should be taken from object mana pool after requirement check.
.SH JSON EXAMPLE
.nf
{
    "value":100,
    "less":true,
    "charge:false
}
.SH XML EXAMPLE
.nf
<mana-req value="100"
	  less="true"
	  charge="false"/>
.SH SEE ALSO
requirements, requirement/mana-percent